Minikube:
=========

    - Access K8s on the Laptop

   - Run K8s locally
   - Run all K8s components in a single node VM
   - Auto download ISO image and create VM
   - Requires Hypervisor
   - Requires kubectl to manage deployments
    


    Minikube:
    =========

    - Install and Run K8s Locally
    - Runs all components of K8s in a single node
    - Download and Install

            - Virtualbox
            - Kubectl
            - Minikube


    minikube.exe start
    minikube status
    kubectl get po
    minikube stop

    
